703167f-a.folder: Bedford Avenue & Sullivan Place, Brooklyn, NY
703167f-a.text:
Bedford Ave., north side, at Sullivan Place, showing the Grandstand of "Ebbets Field".

June 1929.

Eugene L. Armbuster Collection.

706924f-a.folder: Sullivan Place & Bedford Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
706924f-a.text:
Sullivan Place, west from Bedford Ave. A view of Ebbets Field, the baseball grounds of the Brooklyn Dodgers. Pine Place once ran through the center of the grounds.  The Clove Road or "old Road to Bedford" ran the
whole width of the south side of the grounds.
June 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
